window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>The apocalypse is coming. There's only one way off Earth.&nbsp;</p> <p>When a small-moon-sized asteroid is discovered hurtling toward Earth, billionaire scientist Darien Trass must deal with the hardships of finding the select few who will join him on his voyage to escape the apocalypse and rekindle civilization on another world.&nbsp;</p> <p>From the <i>USA Today</i> best-selling author of the Circuit Saga comes this Nebula Award-nominated short story set in his Children of Titan Universe. If you found yourself curious about how the Ringers first came to settle Titan, you won't want to miss this!&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"; 
